  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a <strong>scavenger</strong> in a <strong>post-apocalypse</strong>. With a companion, you explore an <strong>abandoned building complex</strong> in search of a rare resource, <strong>Ordostones</strong>. Be aware that <strong>you are not alone</strong>, as something that brought humanity's world to desolation <strong>stalks you within the fog</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3661380/extras/413e527830364d10c84a3c725d03fea8.avif?t=1756597293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3661380/extras_big/413e527830364d10c84a3c725d03fea8.avif?t=1756597293 width=800 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All you have is a <i>map, night vision, and your companion</i> in a world where <strong>something lurks </strong>to prey on you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Be quick.</strong> <strong>Find the stones.</strong> <strong>And get out of there.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3661380/extras/dba62a1ffb495cfc6ec39e1a5174bbf3.avif?t=1756597293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3661380/extras_big/dba62a1ffb495cfc6ec39e1a5174bbf3.avif?t=1756597293 width=800 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Krysolov</strong> is an <strong>atmospheric</strong> first-person experience in a <strong>post-apocalyptic</strong> future.  </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a <strong>scavenger</strong> in a <strong>post-apocalypse</strong>. With a companion, you explore an <strong>abandoned building complex</strong> in search of a rare resource, <strong>Ordostones</strong>. Be aware that <strong>you are not alone</strong>, as something that brought humanity's world to desolation <strong>stalks you within the fog</strong>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3661380/extras/413e527830364d10c84a3c725d03fea8.avif?t=1756597293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3661380/extras_big/413e527830364d10c84a3c725d03fea8.avif?t=1756597293 width=800 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All you have is a <i>map, night vision, and your companion</i> in a world where <strong>something lurks </strong>to prey on you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Be quick.</strong> <strong>Find the stones.</strong> <strong>And get out of there.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3661380/extras/dba62a1ffb495cfc6ec39e1a5174bbf3.avif?t=1756597293\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3661380/extras_big/dba62a1ffb495cfc6ec39e1a5174bbf3.avif?t=1756597293 width=800 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Krysolov</strong> is an <strong>atmospheric</strong> first-person experience in a <strong>post-apocalyptic</strong> future.  </p>",
